high_descs: Turn around, turn left at the counter, turn left at the window to face the white table.
Pick up the kettle from the table.
Turn left and walk over to the sink on the other side of the room.
Place the kettle inside of the sink, rinse the kettle with water, pick up the kettle.
Turn left and walk to the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Put the kettle down on the counter with the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To rinse a kettle and put it on the counter next to the coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk behind you to the kitchen table on the right side.
Pick up a pot from the table.
Walk around the table to the kitchen sink.
Put the pot in the sink, wash it, then pick it up again.
Walk to the kitchen counter near the coffee maker on your left.
Put the pot in front of the coffee make.
anns.task_desc: Wash a pot and put it near the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white table on your left.
Pick up the silver tea kettle from the table.
Turn back around and go to the sink behind you.
Place the tea kettle in the sink, turn the water on, fill the tea kettle with water, turn off the water, and remove the tea kettle from the sink.
Turn to your left and go to the counter across from you with the coffee maker on it.
Place the tea kettle on the counter, in front of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a teak kettle full of water on the counter.
